ingredients.ingredient: 1 (16 ounce) can Old El Paso® fat-free refried beans
½ cup Old El Paso® Thick 'n Chunky salsa
8 fat free flour tortillas (8 to10 inch)
½ cup shredded Monterey Jack cheese

cookingTips: Mix beans with salsa and chili powder before rolling for even flavor distribution
Arrange seam-side down on baking sheet to prevent unrolling during baking
enrichment.coachingPrompt: Help the user prepare a lighter filling with proper proportions and guide them through careful rolling technique for intact roll-ups.
